1
00:01:32,170 --> 00:01:33,010
Mám ťa rada!

2
00:01:46,460 --> 00:01:48,340
-Vieš...
-Áno?

3
00:01:48,350 --> 00:01:49,710
Si otravná.

4
00:01:49,720 --> 00:01:50,600
A špata.

5
00:01:50,610 --> 00:01:52,320
Nezáujem.

6
00:01:58,870 --> 00:02:01,020
Prepáč, Moe...

7
00:02:01,030 --> 00:02:02,140
Tak ako?

8
00:02:02,150 --> 00:02:05,140
Asi to neskončilo dobre.

9
00:02:05,150 --> 00:02:08,130
Kam ideš, Aoi?

10
00:02:18,630 --> 00:02:19,810
Zavadziaš.

11
00:02:23,290 --> 00:02:26,650
Vieš, koľko odvahy
ju stálo vyznať sa ti?

12
00:02:27,450 --> 00:02:30,060
A ty jej odpovieš takto.
Neuveriteľné.

13
00:02:30,070 --> 00:02:32,050
Nemáš ani právo žiť.

14
00:02:32,060 --> 00:02:33,310
A ty si kto?

15
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:36,200
Kamarátka Moe, Nishimori Aoi.

16
00:02:37,320 --> 00:02:38,030
Moe?

17
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:40,660
Dievča, čo sa ti práve vyznalo!

18
00:02:40,870 --> 00:02:43,900
Moe to tak vážne cíti.

19
00:02:46,900 --> 00:02:48,160
Čo?

20
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:55,180
Aj ty to so mnou chceš?

21
00:03:02,300 --> 00:03:03,980
No to určite!

22
00:03:13,300 --> 00:03:16,700
Au, to bolí.

23
00:03:19,020 --> 00:03:20,330
Jau, moja noha.

24
00:03:20,340 --> 00:03:21,060
Prepáč.

25
00:03:21,070 --> 00:03:25,960
-Bude červená.
-Počkať, počkať!

26
00:03:29,190 --> 00:03:30,550
Dala som to.

27
00:03:30,910 --> 00:03:33,420
Teraz doľava.

28
00:03:42,290 --> 00:03:43,610
Kugayama Shuusei?

29
00:03:47,750 --> 00:03:48,430
Aha, tam je!

30
00:03:48,440 --> 00:03:51,480
-Ten vľavo či vpravo?
-Jasné, že vpravo!

31
00:03:56,470 --> 00:03:57,440
Je úžasný!

32
00:03:57,450 --> 00:03:59,690
A on sa ti páči?

33
00:03:59,700 --> 00:04:01,870
Robíš si srandu?
Je atraktívny.

34
00:04:01,870 --> 00:04:05,150
A nielen kvôli výzoru,
je aj dobrý športovec.

35
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:08,530
To je super...

36
00:04:16,990 --> 00:04:17,650
Teraz hore.

37
00:04:17,660 --> 00:04:18,660
Čo?

38
00:04:19,980 --> 00:04:21,240
Jauvajs...

39
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:23,350
-To už sám vyjdeš, nie?
-Nie.

40
00:04:30,500 --> 00:04:31,430
Ako chceš.

41
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,430
Raz, dva...

42
00:04:36,110 --> 00:04:38,370
Neskočíš do nemocnice, keď ťa tak bolí?

43
00:04:38,370 --> 00:04:39,370
Nie.

44
00:04:39,370 --> 00:04:42,050
-Prečo?
-Nemám nemocnice rád.

45
00:04:49,280 --> 00:04:52,690
Dávaj láskavo pozor.

46
00:04:54,700 --> 00:04:55,910
Prepáč.

47
00:05:09,790 --> 00:05:11,720
Tu sme.

48
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:14,870
Čože?

49
00:05:22,310 --> 00:05:23,490
Prečo tu?

50
00:05:23,620 --> 00:05:25,610
Tu bývam.

51
00:05:25,620 --> 00:05:28,110
Čo?
Aj ja tu bývam.

52
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:29,590
Čo?

53
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:30,280
To fakt?

54
00:05:30,290 --> 00:05:32,350
V ktorej izbe?

55
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:33,410
V tej novej.

56
00:05:33,420 --> 00:05:34,370
Tej oproti?

57
00:05:34,380 --> 00:05:35,370
Odkedy?

58
00:05:35,380 --> 00:05:36,590
Od minulého týždňa.

59
00:05:41,410 --> 00:05:42,360
To nemyslíš vážne.

60
00:05:42,370 --> 00:05:44,370
[Kugayama]

61
00:06:10,770 --> 00:06:13,610
Prečo musím takto trpieť?

62
00:06:22,780 --> 00:06:23,280
Au!

63
00:06:23,960 --> 00:06:24,950
Čo robíš?

64
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:26,950
Však to sú...

65
00:06:26,960 --> 00:06:28,960
Chceš ich vidieť?

66
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:34,160
-Rozhodne nie.
-Kedy bude jedlo?

67
00:06:34,170 --> 00:06:37,090
Teraz upratujem.
Potom navarím.

68
00:06:37,100 --> 00:06:38,340
Au.

69
00:06:38,350 --> 00:06:40,100
Som hladný.

70
00:06:43,370 --> 00:06:45,160
Ten chalan je strašný!

71
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:49,010
[Nishimori]

72
00:06:59,330 --> 00:07:01,750
Prečo tu bývaš?

73
00:07:02,190 --> 00:07:04,370
Už rok bývam sama.

74
00:07:05,080 --> 00:07:06,240
A to prečo?

75
00:07:06,250 --> 00:07:12,590
Minulý rok sa musel otec sťahovať kvôli práci.
Mama s malým bratom šli s ním.

76
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:14,880
Ale ja som chcela zostať.

77
00:07:14,890 --> 00:07:17,800
V škole ti to dovolili,
ale vydržíš to až do výšky?

78
00:07:20,670 --> 00:07:22,260
Si blbá.

79
00:07:22,270 --> 00:07:24,600
Nie som.

80
00:07:27,340 --> 00:07:29,520
Je to ďaleko.

81
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:33,250
No a?

82
00:07:34,810 --> 00:07:37,280
Nechcem prestupovať do inej školy.

83
00:07:37,290 --> 00:07:39,870
Nechcem opustiť Moe.

84
00:07:41,020 --> 00:07:41,630
Moe?

85
00:07:43,450 --> 00:07:45,990
Tá, čo sa ti dnes vyznala.

86
00:07:47,290 --> 00:07:50,870
Moe je milé dievča,
ale to ty vôbec nevidíš.

87
00:07:50,870 --> 00:07:53,570
Ale naozaj.
Na nižšej strednej

88
00:07:53,570 --> 00:07:57,680
ma ostatní šikanovali,
ale ona vždy stála pri mne.

89
00:07:57,690 --> 00:07:59,080
Vyzerá to super.

90
00:07:59,090 --> 00:08:00,670
Vydesil si ma.

91
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:05,060
Obleč sa, prosím ťa!

92
00:08:34,040 --> 00:08:41,690
Jaj, no teda.
Všetko zamočené!

93
00:08:45,470 --> 00:08:49,980
Zavolám opravára.
Bude to v pohode.

94
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:51,660
Prepáčte mi to!

95
00:08:52,970 --> 00:08:55,400
Ako dlho bude trvať oprava?

96
00:08:55,410 --> 00:09:01,150
Ako vidím, kopu vecí budú musieť vymeniť.
Dávam tomu tak týždeň.

97
00:09:01,160 --> 00:09:02,770
Tak dlho?

98
00:09:02,780 --> 00:09:05,410
Kam teraz pôjdeš, Shuusei?

99
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:09,530
Už nemáme voľné apartmány.

100
00:09:09,540 --> 00:09:12,410
U nás máme prázdnu izbu, ale...

101
00:09:12,420 --> 00:09:15,950
To je v pohode, ostanem u kamarátky.

102
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,200
Nevadí to?

103
00:09:17,210 --> 00:09:17,910
Nie.

104
00:09:17,920 --> 00:09:19,120
Však?

105
00:09:19,130 --> 00:09:20,460
Čo?

106
00:09:20,470 --> 00:09:22,800
Akože kde u kamarátky?

107
00:09:26,770 --> 00:09:27,770
U teba.

108
00:09:31,180 --> 00:09:32,190
Čo?!

109
00:09:33,800 --> 00:09:35,870
To fakt?!

110
00:09:37,870 --> 00:09:42,760
L-DK
Preložila Kiyo

111
00:09:49,120 --> 00:09:52,800
<i>- Rekonštrukcia -</i>
<i>Bývam oproti, kontaktujte správcu</i>

112
00:10:07,040 --> 00:10:10,230
Bože, čo som komu urobila?

113
00:10:26,620 --> 00:10:29,210
Prepáč, mám tu neporiadok.

114
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:36,080
Bože!

115
00:10:40,170 --> 00:10:43,380
-Videl si ich?
-Idem do sprchy.

116
00:10:43,380 --> 00:10:45,380
Červené s bielymi bodkami.

117
00:10:55,090 --> 00:11:00,230
Čo teraz?
Nechodíme spolu, ani sa mi nepáči...

118
00:11:09,480 --> 00:11:14,280
Ježiši, počkať!
Prosím ťa, obleč sa!

119
00:11:14,290 --> 00:11:15,860
Však som vnútri, tak čo.

120
00:11:15,870 --> 00:11:17,870
Aké "tak čo"?
Som dievča.

121
00:11:17,880 --> 00:11:20,510
Všetko berieš strašne vážne, no tak.

122
00:11:20,510 --> 00:11:26,370
Nie, ale sú tu pravidlá.
Ak ťa niekto uvidí, budú problémy.

123
00:11:26,380 --> 00:11:28,380
-Mňam!
-To je vážna vec...

124
00:11:30,340 --> 00:11:31,140
Je to super.

125
00:11:54,040 --> 00:11:55,950
Nishimori.

126
00:11:57,290 --> 00:11:59,950
Sú moje hodiny také nudné?

127
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:00,380
Nie.

128
00:12:00,380 --> 00:12:03,220
To vôbec nie.
Prepáčte mi.

129
00:12:06,720 --> 00:12:08,310
Si v pohode?

130
00:12:28,770 --> 00:12:30,440
A čo jeho zranenie?

131
00:12:31,370 --> 00:12:35,690
To je strašné!
Klamár jeden!

132
00:12:35,700 --> 00:12:37,400
Nishimori?

133
00:12:37,410 --> 00:12:40,500
-Kto je klamár?
-Prepáčte.

134
00:12:40,880 --> 00:12:42,420
To je akože čo?

135
00:12:42,870 --> 00:12:44,420
To vôbec nie si ty.

136
00:12:51,850 --> 00:12:53,290
Prečo si na mojom matraci?

137
00:12:53,300 --> 00:12:55,430
Môj zavadzia.
A je tam zima.

138
00:12:55,850 --> 00:13:02,230
No a čo, že tam máš zimu.
Ten je môj, vráť mi ho.

139
00:13:05,320 --> 00:13:06,940
Robí si, čo chce.

140
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:24,960
Dokelu!

141
00:13:29,920 --> 00:13:35,380
Už nemáme čas.
Prídeš neskoro!

142
00:13:35,390 --> 00:13:37,380
Tak vymeškám hodinu.

143
00:13:37,390 --> 00:13:39,980
-Ach nie...
-Máš tu odpadky.

144
00:13:50,240 --> 00:13:53,310
Vieš, mám toho teraz veľa.

145
00:13:53,320 --> 00:13:56,490
Bývať sama je predsa ťažké.

146
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:05,130
Počuj, Moe.

147
00:14:07,750 --> 00:14:10,090
Ten Kugayama...

148
00:14:11,670 --> 00:14:13,840
Páči sa mi ešte viac!

149
00:14:13,970 --> 00:14:15,070
Prečo?

150
00:14:15,080 --> 00:14:16,750
Aj keď bol k tebe taký hnusný?

151
00:14:16,760 --> 00:14:21,430
Hrá sa na štýlového, lebo je to princ.
Vieš, je ako princ Yamashiro...

152
00:14:21,850 --> 00:14:22,870
To fakt?

153
00:14:23,980 --> 00:14:28,140
Niekto tu má malér! To ste počuli,
že Nanami z béčky chcú vyhodiť?

154
00:14:28,150 --> 00:14:30,070
-Vyhodiť zo školy?
-A prečo?

155
00:14:30,070 --> 00:14:32,600
Zistilo sa, že býva s frajerom.

156
00:14:32,610 --> 00:14:35,690
No nie je hlúpa?
Ale vlastne dobre urobili.

157
00:14:35,700 --> 00:14:38,480
Škola ešte stále zasahuje aj do tohto?

158
00:14:38,490 --> 00:14:40,780
Vieš, bývajú s tým problémy.

159
00:14:40,790 --> 00:14:43,360
V škole máme dosť prísny režim.

160
00:14:43,370 --> 00:14:46,570
Takže, Meina.
Musíme si dávať pozor.

161
00:14:46,580 --> 00:14:47,870
Dobre, Hama.

162
00:14:47,880 --> 00:14:50,290
Vy spolu nebývate.

163
00:14:50,300 --> 00:14:53,340
Jasné, vyťahuj sa tu, že si šťastný!
Že sa nehanbíš!

164
00:14:57,010 --> 00:14:58,600
Aha, tam je Shuusei.

165
00:14:59,850 --> 00:15:00,590
Chcem ho ísť pozdraviť!

166
00:15:00,600 --> 00:15:03,270
Ale nebude to blbé, keď ťa odmietol?

167
00:15:03,270 --> 00:15:04,770
-Neviem, či tam ísť.
-No...

168
00:15:06,770 --> 00:15:07,900
Bacha, ide sem.

169
00:15:13,990 --> 00:15:14,490
Hej.

170
00:15:15,490 --> 00:15:16,310
Áno?

171
00:15:16,320 --> 00:15:17,530
Tamtá.

172
00:15:22,120 --> 00:15:22,870
Ja?

173
00:15:22,870 --> 00:15:24,370
Tu máš kľúč.

174
00:15:25,990 --> 00:15:27,590
Počkať, počkať!

175
00:15:30,670 --> 00:15:32,110
Úplne som naho zabudla.

176
00:15:33,510 --> 00:15:34,970
Už s tým prestaň!

177
00:15:38,370 --> 00:15:41,140
Ak to v škole zistia, vyhodia nás.

178
00:15:41,270 --> 00:15:43,010
A kvôli komu sa to deje?

179
00:15:43,020 --> 00:15:46,870
To je teraz jedno, ale budú s tým
problémy a môžu nás vyhodiť...

180
00:15:46,870 --> 00:15:47,870
Takže ho nechceš?

181
00:15:47,870 --> 00:15:49,060
Daj mi ho.

182
00:15:50,170 --> 00:15:52,480
Tak dáš mi ho?

183
00:15:57,670 --> 00:15:58,660
A čo "ďakujem"?

184
00:15:59,870 --> 00:16:01,830
Nie, prestaň!

185
00:16:05,410 --> 00:16:07,050
Ak to zistia, bude zle, však?

186
00:16:09,080 --> 00:16:11,500
-Tak ďakujem.
-Nepočujem.

187
00:16:13,450 --> 00:16:14,670
Ďakujem!

188
00:16:16,760 --> 00:16:17,770
Dobrá práca.

189
00:16:21,870 --> 00:16:25,020
Tá noha sa ti kedy zahojila?

190
00:16:25,770 --> 00:16:26,870
Ktovie.

191
00:16:26,870 --> 00:16:29,650
To nemyslíš vážne!

192
00:16:30,900 --> 00:16:32,120
Shuusei!

193
00:16:34,820 --> 00:16:37,950
Shuusei, konečne to máme.

194
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:38,900
Babu?

195
00:16:38,910 --> 00:16:43,080
Nemáš dobrú náladu, čo?
Lebo som bol na zoznamovacej párty?

196
00:16:43,090 --> 00:16:45,080
Ale nie.

197
00:16:45,090 --> 00:16:47,320
Nie, nie, niečo sa stalo, čo?

198
00:16:47,330 --> 00:16:50,740
Včera na teba Yune čakala.

199
00:16:50,750 --> 00:16:51,710
Čo?
A kde?

200
00:16:53,870 --> 00:16:57,570
-Aoi, čo to má znamenať?
-Vy so Shuuseiom...

201
00:16:57,570 --> 00:16:59,830
Kľúč, kľúč!
Vypadol mi kľúč, viete?

202
00:16:59,840 --> 00:17:01,840
No nie je milý?

203
00:17:01,840 --> 00:17:02,990
To teda.

204
00:17:03,000 --> 00:17:03,810
Je super, že?

205
00:17:03,820 --> 00:17:06,370
Je proste úžasný.

206
00:17:09,440 --> 00:17:11,020
[Nebehaj tu nahý!]

207
00:17:11,020 --> 00:17:12,670
[Zásoby na celý mesiac - nejesť!]

208
00:17:12,670 --> 00:17:14,870
[Pred vstupom do kúpeľne zaklop!]
[Bez povolenia neotvárať.]

209
00:17:21,320 --> 00:17:23,980
Nechcem Moe klamať.

210
00:17:29,410 --> 00:17:30,870
Hotovo!

211
00:17:30,880 --> 00:17:33,290
A tu je môj priestor!

212
00:17:37,340 --> 00:17:38,590
Teraz uvidíš.

213
00:17:42,590 --> 00:17:43,130
Čože?

214
00:17:43,140 --> 00:17:45,140
Čo teraz?

215
00:17:34,540 --> 00:17:35,570
Som späť.

216
00:17:46,680 --> 00:17:47,860
Aj zámku máš super.

217
00:17:49,600 --> 00:17:50,100
No poď.

218
00:17:53,100 --> 00:17:54,500
Pekné.

219
00:17:54,510 --> 00:17:56,980
Pre jedného tak akurát.

220
00:17:56,990 --> 00:17:59,980
No toto!

221
00:17:59,990 --> 00:18:01,820
Babské prádlo!

222
00:18:04,320 --> 00:18:06,770
To je susedkine.

223
00:18:06,780 --> 00:18:09,040
Bola si u mňa prať.

224
00:18:09,450 --> 00:18:10,130
Aká je?

225
00:18:12,950 --> 00:18:14,980
Taká s červeným spodným prádlom.

226
00:18:14,990 --> 00:18:17,590
Fakt?
A čo je to za babu?

227
00:18:19,400 --> 00:18:20,120
Obyčajné dievča.

228
00:18:20,130 --> 00:18:21,550
Od nás zo školy?

229
00:18:22,800 --> 00:18:23,840
Kto, kto?

230
00:18:27,600 --> 00:18:30,220
Ako sa len volá...

231
00:18:33,770 --> 00:18:34,770
Nepočul si nič?

232
00:18:34,780 --> 00:18:36,980
Nie.

233
00:18:38,400 --> 00:18:42,460
Ale je to dobré mať susedku, čo?

234
00:18:42,870 --> 00:18:44,170
Nie je na tom nič zvláštne.

235
00:18:44,170 --> 00:18:45,950
Nič zvláštne?

236
00:18:45,950 --> 00:18:48,560
Napríklad, keď sneží.
"Požičal by si mi dáždnik?"

237
00:18:48,570 --> 00:18:50,830
Alebo keď sa vymkne.
"Môžem byť chvíľu u teba?"

238
00:18:50,840 --> 00:18:53,680
"Uvarila som večeru, prídeš?"
Také veci nič?

239
00:19:04,050 --> 00:19:05,390
Nechaj ma!

240
00:19:08,430 --> 00:19:10,180
Počul som dievčenský hlas.

241
00:19:10,190 --> 00:19:12,820
To sa asi vedľa kúpu.

242
00:19:12,820 --> 00:19:13,370
To fakt?

243
00:19:13,370 --> 00:19:15,780
Tu sa dá počuť do ich kúpeľne?

244
00:19:15,780 --> 00:19:16,410
Možno.

245
00:19:16,690 --> 00:19:17,990
Pardon...

246
00:19:23,370 --> 00:19:24,170
Čo je?

247
00:19:24,170 --> 00:19:26,530
O čo sa snažíš?

248
